docs {
  # Search By SAN & CPE Serial Number Journey
  
  Tujuan:
    1. "Order X itu SAN & CPE Serial Number-nya apa?"           â†’ 01-By-Order-ID
    2. "SAN 23532557 dipakai di sales order mana saja?"          â†’ 02-By-SAN
    3. "cpeSerialNumber TK3B119002209-test dipakai di order mana?" â†’ 03-By-CPE-Serial
    4. (bonus) "Inventory ID-nya apa?" â†’ di-capture otomatis di chain
  
  -----------------------------------------------------------------
  Actual structure di dalam response order (dari pengamatan live
  di `https://mobily-dev2.live.demo-in.telflow.com/portal/api/order/order/...`):
  
    {
      ...
      "Characteristic": { "ID": "san" },
      "Value": "23532557"
    },
    {
      "Characteristic": { "ID": "cpeSerialNumber" },
      "Value": "TK3B119002209-test"
    }
  
  â†’ Keduanya tersimpan sebagai **nested Characteristic** (bukan top-level field).
  -----------------------------------------------------------------
  
  Swagger TIDAK menyediakan parameter khusus `characteristicId=san&value=...`.
  Query params yang tersedia untuk cross-search di salesorders/customerorders/inventory:
  
  | endpoint          | parameter yang relevan              |
  |-------------------|-------------------------------------|
  | /v1/salesorders   | q, customerReference, externalReferenceId, customerId |
  | /v1/customerorders| q, inventoryId, customerReference, externalReferenceId, customerId, relatedBusinessInteractionID |
  | /v1/inventory     | q, name, externalReferenceId, businessInteractionId, specificationName, type, class |
  
  â†’ Strategi pencarian yang bekerja:
  
  **Strategy A â€” Free-text `q` (cepat, tapi bergantung index)**
    GET /portal/api/v1/salesorders?q=23532557&verbose=true
    GET /portal/api/v1/customerorders?q=23532557&verbose=true
    (Telflow text index biasanya meng-index characteristic value juga.
     Kalau 0 hasil â†’ index belum cover characteristic â†’ pakai Strategy B.)
  
  **Strategy B â€” Via Inventory (reliable, multi-hop)**
    1. Cari inventory dengan q=<value>            â†’ dapat inventoryId
    2. GET inventory/{id}/relationships           â†’ list BusinessInteractions
    3. GET customerorders?inventoryId=<id>        â†’ direct match
    4. Untuk SalesOrders, fetch each BI ID dari step 2
       (salesorders tidak punya `inventoryId` param, tapi bisa via relationships).
  
  -----------------------------------------------------------------
  Real base path: `/portal/api/v1/...` (bukan `/api/v1/...`).
  Detail order pakai endpoint dedicated Portal: `/portal/api/order/order/{id}`.
  -----------------------------------------------------------------
  
  Folder:
  
  ### 01-By-Order-ID â€” lookup SAN/CPE dari orderId
    01 - Get Order Detail (Portal)  â† exact URL spt live system
    02 - Get Customer Order (v1 swagger-style)
    03 - Get Customer Order Relationships
    04 - Get Sales Order
    05 - Get Sales Order Items
  
  ### 02-By-SAN â€” reverse lookup by SAN value
    01 - Search Sales Orders by q (SAN)          â† PRIMARY fast path
    02 - Search Customer Orders by q (SAN)
    03 - Search Inventory by SAN                 â† capture inventoryId
    04 - Get Inventory Detail
    05 - Get Inventory Relationships             â† list related BI (orders)
    06 - List Customer Orders by inventoryId     â† direct match by inventory
  
  ### 03-By-CPE-Serial â€” reverse lookup by cpeSerialNumber value
    01 - Search Sales Orders by q (CPE Serial)
    02 - Search Customer Orders by q (CPE Serial)
    03 - Search Inventory by CPE Serial          â† capture inventoryId
    04 - Get Inventory Detail
    05 - Get Inventory Relationships
    06 - List Customer Orders by inventoryId
}

